{"title":"新安江诗抄——献给在建设岗位上的战友们","authors":["蔡庆生"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新安江诗抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给在建设岗位上的战友们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡庆生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勘测队长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜深啦！夜深啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的队长那里去了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工棚里留了个空床位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜他在那里睡觉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下午水位急速上升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻探机不能继续钻进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他守着机器盼水位下降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫长夜在为任务担心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设计员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭时常把筷子停下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘，这几天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为啥心情不宁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为啥食欲不振？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上迟迟不睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜常常惊醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了蓝图上的一寸线姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你像得了病。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警报器已经响了两遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在山头左右摇摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山炮马上就要轰鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路上行人已断绝往来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全员带着一面红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡逻在警戒区的边缘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了保证别人的安全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他工作的地方最危险。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}